# Frontend Component Structure

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[app/page.tsx] --> B[SearchBar Component]
    A --> C[ForceGraph Component]
    A --> D[NodeDetails Component]
    A --> E[LoadingState Component]

    B --> F[usePaperSearch Hook]
    F --> G[Fetch API: /api/search]

    G --> H{API Response}
    H -->|Success| I[Update Graph State]
    H -->|Error| J[Display Error Message]

    I --> C
    C --> K[react-force-graph-2d]
    K --> L[Custom Node Rendering]
    K --> M[Interaction Handlers]

    M --> N[handleNodeClick]
    N --> D

    D --> O[Display Paper Details]
    O --> P[Title, Authors, Citations]

    style A fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style C fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style D fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style E fill:#FF4400,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFF
    style K fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
```

**组件说明**:
- **SearchBar**: Rams 风格搜索框（白/灰/橙配色）
- **ForceGraph**: 力导向图可视化（简单圆形节点）
- **NodeDetails**: 论文详情面板（极简布局）
- **LoadingState**: 加载状态指示器（无动画或微妙动画）
